title: Team looking for D5+ Top/Mid who is aged between 14 and 20
body:
Hey there!

We are looking for a Top/Mid who is atleast Diamond V and motivated to play in our team. We will be playing in a League in which you can win money.
Things you should have:
-Time, about 3 scrims per week from 8pm CET and Tournament Games aswell as more scrims on weekend!
-Working headset, we will be using discord
-Shotcalling
-Tilt proof

If you are interested in playing in our team I would be very happy and you can add me on the league client 
(SearchingMembers) and we can talk.

Thank you for your time 

Greetings
"SearchingMembers"
